{
  "stem": "13258.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The mail came to my house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother went and bought a-- an Easter egg from paper-- which you could put together, put some candy in there-- put the letter on the bottom, put the candy on top, gave me the Easter egg, said, get on the bus, ride out to the barracks, and say-- see that you deliver it to what they call Werkmeister Rosenzweig.",
      "word_count": 60
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, I, I got there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was a guard in front of the barracks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And a little guy-- little kid comes in and says-- I was 10 years old about at the time-- I have a Easter egg for Werkmeister Rosenzweig.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He said, go ahead, go ahead, and pointed which building it was.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I brought him the Easter egg.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that was my first involvement in conspiracy against Hitler.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He get-- he subsequently quit the police in, in Beuthen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he got to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I know-- and my aunt who had met him-- my aunt who lives in, in Israel, as a matter of fact-- I saw from some letters I found lately that she had heard of him, that he had gotten to Israel, and was in the police.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Or some-- not-- yeah, she was-- he was in the British police school where he was being trained together with Arabs to be in the British police in Palestine.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1933, in spring.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And again, this is to me anecdotal, the, the-- some of the details.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because at the time-- 11 years old or 12, shortly before my 12th birthday-- I didn't understand all the--",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--goings on.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father was called to the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Apparently, they had not liked some of the things he had written in the paper.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
